+-------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| `Localization`_   | New (introduced v1.5) Localization domain interfaces and classes                                             |
+-------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| `StorageUtils`_   | Business interfaces and classes to abstract storage access (remover, saver, updater, repositories, etc)      |
